quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  11,6,There is no moving creature on earth whose provision is not guaranteed by God. And He knows where it lives and where it is laid to rest. All is ňĻwrittenňļ in a perfect Record
  11,7,"He is the One Who created the heavens and the earth in six Days‚ÄĒand His Throne was upon the waters‚ÄĒin order to test which of you is best in deeds. And if you ňĻO Prophetňļ say, ‚ÄúSurely you will ňĻallňļ be raised up after death,‚ÄĚ the disbelievers will certainly say, ‚ÄúThat is nothing but pure magic!‚ÄĚ"
